Class QueueMM1N

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    JMarkovElement

    public class QueueMM1N
extends SimpleMarkovProcess<examples.jmarkov.QueueMM1NState,examples.jmarkov.QueueMM1NEvent>
    This class implements an M/M/1/N queue. That is a single server exponential queue with Poisson Arrivals. It extends SimpleMarkovProcess.
    Version:
    1.0a
    Author:
    Germán Riaño. Universidad de los Andes.
